Mun. of Poconé. Highway Poconé - Porto Cercado Approx. at km 17, near Fazenda Macaco. Seasonally inundated earthmound (murundum) savanna. The elevated murunduns are grown by Cerrado trees and shrubs and dominated by Curatella americana, the seasonally inundated grassy campo is dominated by Paspalum stellatum, Panicum stenodes and Andropogon selloanus. Campo is completely dried up (almost)
